window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>An empire in flames. A prisoner of war. An unbreakable will to escape.</b></p> <p>At just 15, Eskara Helsene fought in the greatest war mankind has ever known - and lost. There is only one place her enemies would send a Sourcerer as powerful as her: the Pit, a prison sunk so deep into the earth the sun is a distant memory. Now, she finds herself stripped of her magic; a young girl surrounded by thieves, murderers, and worse. In order to survive she will need to make new allies, play the inmates against each other, and find a way out.</p> <p>Her enemies will soon find out that Eskara is not so easily broken.</p>"; 
